{"tid":425354,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇唔到前路","createTime":"2017-10-05T16:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T18:16:48.000Z","uid":1469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f54da42087301ea7c50a4e6ceb235ee665fd488b","tid":425354,"uid":1469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2e64c5178546ac834530251511a95fe6cac48f","tid":425354,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"你老母當初比隻狗破左處 <br />\n最後生撚埋你出黎 <br />\n記唔記得呀 <br />\n你老豆係我執返黎架 <br />\n無我大慈大悲 <br />\n你伯爺仲係街度食緊人地d屎ja世侄 <br />\n諗起你岩岩出世個撚樣唔人唔狗咁 <br />\n我而家都吱一聲咁笑出黎 <br />\n契爺我睇住你大 <br />\n你而家走黎我屋企門口 <br />\n又痾屎又痾尿盛臭架嘛世侄 <br />\n真係狗娘養的(笑)"},{"pid":"f02d6786b3778e3b779cc6dfe276936865d023d9","tid":425354,"uid":91978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"你依家知道都未遲 加油 如果真係唔鐘意讀書 或者出黎做野都係一個好選擇"},{"pid":"c6d40c04897d676efed627681154721ff04ca871","tid":425354,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490fa43b117ba01f12c281d8cc5366065c13cad7","tid":425354,"uid":1469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經浪費左1年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582c44c10def578a764b8e5cebec7842703bdefd","tid":425354,"uid":135205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"絲打幾歲先？有無咩目標？無嘅話可以試下做住野先慢慢搵目標 兩年前同你情況差唔多 出黎做做下野先搵到目標 想做個份職業係要讀上去嘅 但我讀書屎 個陣都怕浪費時間同錢唔敢重新讀書 但比朋友屌醒 浪費幾年算係咩 最緊要係搵到同做到想做嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid